sentence: The following companies are expected to report earnings prior to market open on 10/25/2013.
Visit our Earnings Calendar for a full list of expected earnings releases.
Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ) is reporting for the quarter ending September 30, 2013.
The cleaning company's consensus earnings per share forecast from the 14 analysts that follow the stock is $1.05.
This value represents a 0.94% decrease compared to the same quarter last year.
In the past year PG has beat the expectations every quarter.
The highest one was in the 2nd calendar quarter where they beat the consensus by 2.6%.
Zacks Investment Research reports that the 2014 Price to Earnings ratio for PG is 18.86 vs. an industry ratio of 20.30.
